	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Legate under Antony (Vell. 2.82.2-3), who followed the main force bringing supplies and a siege train, but his forces and machines were destroyed by the Parthians (Vell. 2.82.2; Plut. Ant. 38; Dio 49.25.2-26.1, and 44.2; Zonar. 10.26)." .
